Location wise its on a fairly quiet street perfect for Midtown, 5th Avenue, Central Park and Times Square - for venturing further we never had more than a minute wait in hailing a cab.	Room felt very quiet for the city as it is on a 2 lane street -- some traffic noise but nothing that was prevented a pleasant stay.	Even though we were so close to 5th Ave shopping and Time Square chaos, it was quiet enough to get a good night sleep.